{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ad nehme wiſſi Laudis\nno Juhda. Usiju / tas\npats bija fefchpadeſmits\nGaddus wezz/ un darrija to par\nKehninu winna Tehwa Amazi-\njus Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas uſtaisija Elatu/ un\natdabbuja to attak pee Juhdu/\npehz kad tas Kehninsch ar fa-\nweem Tehweem bija atsmidſts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Gefchpadeſmits Gaddus\nwezz bija Usijus/ kad tas par\nKehninu tappe/ un waldija peez-\ndefinits un divi Gaddus Jeru-\nfaleimê/ un winna Mahtei bija\nJekaltija Wahrdâ no Jerufalemes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſsch darrija/ kaſt tam\nKiNGAM labbi patikke / itt\nka winna Tehws Amazius bij\ndarrijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiſsch mekleja Deewu/\nkamehr Sakarijas dſihwoja/ kas\nfaprattigs bija ceſſch Deewa\nParahdifchanahm / kamehr tas\nnu to KiNGU mekleja/ tad likke\nDeews tam labbi isdohtees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo wiſsch iſgahje un kar-\nroja prett teem Wilistereem/ un\nnolausija to Muhri no Gattas /\nun to Muhri no Jabnes/ un to\nMuhri no Asdodas/ un uſtais-\nja Pilsfahthus Asdodas ( Wal-\nſti)/ un ſarp teem Wilistereem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews palihdſeja tam\nprett teem Wilistereem/ un prett\nteein Arabereem / kas Gur Ba-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Ammoniteri de-\nUsijam Dahwanas / un win-\nSlava tspaude lihds Egip-\nRohbeschabm / jo wiſsch tap\njo Deenas jo watak warrens\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Usijus darrija arrids\nTurkus Jerufaleimê/ pee tah\nStuhra Wahrtim / un pee O\nleijas Wahrtim / un pee zitte\nStuhreem/ un apſtiprinaja to\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſsch uſtaisija arrids\nTurkus Lukſuefi / un isra-\ndauds Akkas/ jo winnam b\ndauds Lohpu / tik labbi Elei-\nka Klatjumôs/ ir Arraji un W\nna-Dahrsneeki us Kalneem\naugligeem Tibrunneem/ jo win-\neemihſeja to Semmes Darbu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehl bija Usijus Ka-\nSpehks ismahzitu Lauschu /\nKarxâ gahje pa Pulkeem/ itti-\ntee lihdſinati ktua zaur Jeielu\nRaſtitaju/ un Maeseju to l\nraugu appakſch Ananija ta K\nnixa Leel-Runga Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi Pulki to Wirf-\nfu to Tehwo Namina/ kas n-\nrent Karra-Wihri bija / bija\nwituhkſtochi un fefchſints.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un appakſch winnu D-\nkas bija Karra-Spehks no tr-\nfints reift tuhkſtoscheem un-\ntix tuhkſtoscheem un peezſinte-\nfas ar warrenn Spehku us k-\nru bija ismahziti / ka tee-\nKehninam prett Eenatdneek-\npalihdſetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Usijus likke teem\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
